description:
Astro Bot features special levels that pay homage to iconic PlayStation franchise. We recommend not watching if you plan to play Astro Bot and want to experience these moments for yourself.

Timestamps:
00:00 - Apes On The Loose (Ape Escape)
08:49 - Bot Of War (God of War Ragnarök)
21:35 - Dude Raiding (Uncharted)
31:35 - Going Loco (LocoRoco)
37:07 - Machine Learning (Horizon Forbidden West)
title: Astro Bot All PlayStation "Hero" Homage Levels [SPOILERS]
